---
title: "US28 — Browse expert categories"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ExpertsScreen (category chips)
  participant C as «Control»<br/>LoadExperts
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertCategory · ExpertProfile
  A->>B: open Experts tab
  B->>C: loadCategories()
  C->>E: listExpertCategories()
  E-->>C: List (ExpertCategory)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (category chips)
  B-->>A: specialty chips
  A->>B: tap a category chip
  B->>C: loadExperts(categoryId)
  C->>E: listExperts(categoryId)
  E-->>C: List (ExpertProfile)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (filtered)
  B-->>A: experts for that specialty
  note over E: planned — listExpertCategories / listExperts<br/>via SupabaseGateway (RLS)
